description.en: ELEPHANT.MONEY has been developed by Bankteller, lead developer and founder of Bankroll Network. ELEPHANT.MONEY implements a voluntary, sustainable, and permissionless global economic engine on top of the bDollar Protocol, BNB, and Bitcoin. The ELEPHANT.MONEY protocol is a 100% complete and finished product and it is designed as a cooperative with 10% dues paid out to holders over the short and long term.
